@{ \\name Calculation Methods
! Compute the matrix \\f$B\\f$ of the \\f$BDB\\f$ operator
! The method computes the matrix \\f$B\\f$ of the \\f$BDB\\f$ operator
! which, in the case of a 2D electrostatic field,
! is given  by
